      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The vehicle features a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring mechanical longevity and structural rigidity. Suspension remains tight with factory-spec damping, while the braking system retains its original bite. An excellent example of a driver-focused machine with a solid service history and no mechanical compromises.",
